{"id":2070,"date":"2021-03-24T22:51:56","date_gmt":"2021-03-24T22:51:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/?p=2070"},"modified":"2021-10-07T04:23:15","modified_gmt":"2021-10-07T04:23:15","slug":"tra-saffron-uong-luc-nao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/tra-saffron-uong-luc-nao\/","title":{"rendered":"B\u00ed quy\u1ebft u\u1ed1ng Saffron h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/saffron\/\">Saffron<\/a> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho c\u1ea3 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 nhan s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. V\u1eady<\/span><b> u\u1ed1ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe kh\u00f4ng? U\u1ed1ng saffron c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Lifenest.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>U\u1ed1ng saffron h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saffron hay nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00fd hi\u1ebfm, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &#8220;v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ecf&#8221;. D\u00f9 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1edfi n\u00f3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe. H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ec7nh nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 kinh ni\u00ean, suy gi\u1ea3m tr\u00ed nh\u1edb, c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh huy\u1ebft \u00e1p v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 tim m\u1ea1ch, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ti\u1ec1n kinh nguy\u1ec7t,&#8230; \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, saffron c\u00f2n l\u00e0 &#8220;th\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee3c&#8221; trong ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm gi\u00fap ph\u00e1i n\u1eef g\u00ecn gi\u1eef n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p thanh xu\u00e2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2072\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2072\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2072\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-13.jpg\" alt=\"saffron nhuy hoa nghe tay 13\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-13.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-13-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-13-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2072\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">U\u1ed1ng saffron h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng? <\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">U\u1ed1ng saffron h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/saffron\/\">nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/a> ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Theo ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a 10-15 s\u1ee3i saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 3 gram\/th\u00e1ng. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a 15-20 s\u1ee3i saffron\/ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 9 gram\/th\u00e1ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>N\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o trong ng\u00e0y?<\/b><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2073\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2073\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2073\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tea.jpg\" alt=\"saffron nhuy hoa nghe tay tea\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tea.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tea-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tea-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2073\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng saffron t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng sau khi th\u1ee9c d\u1eady v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7\u00a0<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>U\u1ed1ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> v\u00e0o th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0o s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t? C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u cho r\u1eb1ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng saffron v\u00e0o t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y (tr\u1eeb nh\u1eefng l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3i) \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng s\u1edbm v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t ly s\u1eefa saffron hay m\u1ed9t ly tr\u00e0 n\u00f3ng saffron v\u00e0o b\u1eefa s\u00e1ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd h\u1ea5p thu c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb saffron m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng, mang \u0111\u1ebfn ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, gi\u00fap tinh th\u1ea7n minh m\u1eabn v\u00e0 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o h\u01a1n khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t ly saffron v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 kho\u1ea3ng 30-40 ph\u00fat s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 sung n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. X\u00f3a tan c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 s\u00e2u v\u00e0 ngon h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng saffron v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, gi\u00fap da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>U\u1ed1ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch g\u00ec?<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, u\u1ed1ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ung th\u01b0\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2074\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2074\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2074\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tea2.jpg\" alt=\"saffron nhuy hoa nghe tay tea2\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tea2.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tea2-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tea2-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2074\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">U\u1ed1ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh ung th\u01b0\u00a0<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc cho bi\u1ebft, trong nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 croin, picrocrotin, safranal, crocetin,&#8230; gi\u00fap \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ung th\u01b0. Ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n ch\u00fang l\u00e2y lan v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o m\u00f4 l\u00e0nh kh\u00e1c. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u0103n b\u1ec7nh nh\u01b0 ung th\u01b0 c\u1ed5 t\u1eed cung, ung th\u01b0 v\u00fa, ung th\u01b0 d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y,&#8230;\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ee9ng tr\u1ea7m c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 suy gi\u1ea3m tr\u00ed nh\u1edb<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 flavonoids, tanin, alkaloids,&#8230; gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t d\u1eabn truy\u1ec1n th\u1ea7n kinh trong n\u00e3o. C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng hao h\u1ee5t ch\u1ea5t serotonin, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh g\u00e2y ra b\u1ec7nh tr\u1ea7m c\u1ea3m.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n crocetin, croin,&#8230; c\u00f3 trong saffron c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi nh\u1edb, s\u1ea3n sinh v\u00e0 li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o th\u1ea7n kinh ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, gi\u00fap tinh th\u1ea7n lu\u00f4n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Gi\u00fap \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ec7 tim m\u1ea1ch\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2075\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2075\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2075\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tim-mach.jpg\" alt=\"saffron nhuy hoa nghe tay tim mach\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tim-mach.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tim-mach-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tim-mach-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2075\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y gi\u00fap \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ec7 tim m\u1ea1ch cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam trong nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 h\u01a1n cho m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh. Gi\u00fap t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p thu kali, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 tim m\u1ea1ch tr\u00e1nh x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, lo \u00e2u k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/thanh-phan-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay\/\">th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n trong nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/a> c\u00f2n gi\u00fap h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m cholesterol, gi\u00fap h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng x\u01a1 v\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 huy\u1ebft \u00e1p cao. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng khi\u1ebfn cho lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y d\u00f9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 t\u00ecm mua.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng trong n\u00e2ng cao s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c l\u00e0n da. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n, ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam t\u1ed1t, nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n, x\u00f3a th\u00e2m v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i vitamin v\u00e0 protein c\u00f3 trong saffron gi\u00fap k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n sinh ra collagen gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. Tyrosinase trong nh\u1ee5y hoa c\u1ea7n t\u00e2y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sinh ra c\u00e1c h\u1eafc s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 melanin gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i x\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 tia UV trong \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi, kh\u00f3i b\u1ee5i,&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>G\u1ee3i \u00fd 3 c\u00e1ch u\u1ed1ng nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 c\u00e1ch u\u1ed1ng nh\u1ee5y hoa ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>D\u00f9ng saffron v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1874\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1874\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1874\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-9.jpg\" alt=\"saffron nhuy hoa nghe tay 9\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-9.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-9-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-9-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1874\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saffron c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch <\/span><b>u\u1ed1ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng theo c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/saffron-tri-mat-ngu\/\">c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7<\/a>, r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n kinh nguy\u1ec7t hay t\u0103ng huy\u1ebft \u00e1p. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, u\u1ed1ng saffron \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ea3 10-15 s\u1ee3i saffron v\u00e0o trong kho\u1ea3ng 200-500ml n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m \u1edf nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 60-70 \u0111\u1ed9 C.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1edd kho\u1ea3ng 5 ph\u00fat cho saffron tan ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ngay m\u1ed9t c\u1ed1c n\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi tr\u00e0 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t. N\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f2n \u1ea5m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e8n ho\u1eb7c m\u1eadt ong \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch v\u1ecb gi\u00e1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><b>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng saffron c\u00f9ng s\u1eefa<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng s\u1eefa mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9c u\u1ed1ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u01a1m ngon v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng. Lo\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc u\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u nguy c\u01a1 m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh tim m\u1ea1ch, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ch\u1ee9ng huy\u1ebft \u00e1p cao, gi\u00fap t\u0103ng tu\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n m\u00e1u n\u00e3o v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 lo\u00e3ng x\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, saffron k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng s\u1eefa c\u00f2n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon v\u00e0 s\u00e2u h\u01a1n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tinh th\u1ea7n lu\u00f4n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, t\u1ef1 tin.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb 1 c\u1ed1c s\u1eefa \u1ea5m\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ea3 3-5 s\u1ee3i saffron v\u00e0o trong c\u1ed1c v\u00e0 ch\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. N\u00ean u\u1ed1ng saffron k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng s\u1eefa v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 30 ph\u00fat v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><b>Saffron k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p m\u1eadt ong<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1873\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1873\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1873\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-8.jpg\" alt=\"saffron nhuy hoa nghe tay 8\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-8.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-8-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-8-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1873\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saffron k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p m\u1eadt ong\u00a0<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong m\u1eadt ong c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao ch\u1ea5t kho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i vitamin. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p b\u1edfi m\u1eadt ong c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa m\u1eadt ong v\u00e0 nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y mang \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng gan, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00ed nh\u1edb, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p da,&#8230;\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cho 3-5 s\u1ee3i saffron v\u00e0o 1 c\u1ed1c n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m, ch\u1edd trong kho\u1ea3ng 5 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 cho saffron tan h\u1ebft.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau \u0111\u00f3, cho kho\u1ea3ng 1-2 th\u00eca m\u1eadt ong (t\u00f9y v\u00e0o kh\u1ea9u v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi) v\u00e0o trong c\u1ed1c l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c ngay.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, <\/span><b>u\u1ed1ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p. H\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng saffron hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Saffron \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho c\u1ea3 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 nhan s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. V\u1eady u\u1ed1ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe kh\u00f4ng? U\u1ed1ng saffron c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Lifenest.\u00a0 U\u1ed1ng saffron h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2076,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_seopress_robots_primary_cat":"none"},"categories":[20],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2070"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2070"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2070\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3951,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2070\/revisions\/3951"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2076"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2070"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2070"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2070"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}